CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773774690
OL,3,CHolyrood set for knife-edge vote on
OL,4,Cwhether to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FGroups in the medical profession,
OL,7,Fincluding the Royal College of
OL,8,FPsychiatrists (RCS) and Royal
OL,9,FPharmaceutical Society, have made
OL,10,Fclear their opposition to the Bill.
OL,12,FEarlier, Deputy First Minister Kate
OL,13,FForbes urged MSPs to consider their
OL,14,Fviews.
OL,16,FForbes said: "I will vote against
OL,17,FAssisted Dying because the Bill is now
OL,18,Friskier and less safe after MSPs
OL,19,Frejected critical safeguards and
OL,20,Foutsourced essential protections for
OL,21,Fdoctors to the UK government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
