OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773774690
OL,3,CHolyrood set for knife-edge vote on
OL,4,Cwhether to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Doctors, psychiatrists, pharmacists
OL,12,Fand palliative care specialists ` the
OL,13,Fpeople who would be tasked with
OL,14,Fimplementing this ` are asking us not
OL,15,Fto do it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
