CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773774690
OL,3,CHolyrood set for knife-edge vote on
OL,4,Cwhether to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,F"These are the people on the front
OL,7,Fline of compassion in Scotland, the
OL,8,Fpeople who have dedicated their lives
OL,9,Fand careers to helping people in life
OL,10,Fand in death. They think this Bill is
OL,11,Funsafe."
OL,13,FDr Gordon Macdonald, chief executive
OL,14,Fof campaign group Care Not Killing,
OL,15,Finsisted such legislation "offers a
OL,16,Fvision of the future which has no
OL,17,Fplace in a caring Scottish society".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
