PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773774690
OL,3,CHolyrood set for knife-edge vote on
OL,4,Cwhether to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FHe added: "Parliament's first
OL,7,Fresponsibility is to protect its most
OL,8,Fvulnerable citizens from exploitation
OL,9,Fand abuse by those who may have a
OL,10,Ffinancial or emotional interest in
OL,11,Ftheir deaths".
OL,13,FHowever, Emma Cooper, convener of
OL,14,Fcampaign group, Friends at the End
OL,15,F(Fate), said: "The vast majority of
OL,16,Fpeople in every single constituency
OL,17,Facross Scotland are asking for
OL,18,Fassisted dying to be made available to
OL,19,Fthose who are mentally competent and
OL,20,Fin the last six months of their life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
