PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773774690
OL,3,CHolyrood set for knife-edge vote on
OL,4,Cwhether to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,F"We cannot deny those who are going to
OL,7,Fdie the right to choose. It is simply
OL,8,Fa misconception that pain relief can
OL,9,Falleviate the suffering of all
OL,10,Fconditions at the end of life."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
